<br />

<br />
My questions are this:
<br />

<br />
Is all that he said true about the cost and medding?
<br />

<br />
Also I thought the more expensive they are the faster they go.  If thats the case would it be worth spending 10K for a slow ride?
<br />

<br />
Thanks for anyone who can answer these.</span></td>
