				<td colspan="2"><span>Well yes, you do med while standing there, or riding at full speed, that's true, and mobs don't consider you sitting (you can cast too) so that's the benefits to horses/lizards.
<br />

<br />
As for speed, they do get faster as you spend more.  To the best of my knowledge, we can smoke the 100k version.  I don't have one, but know that the 10k version isn't much faster if any than JBoots <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-13.gif" border="0" alt="LOL" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
So if you have one, and Run 3, get off the horse to get anywhere fast...
<br />

