				<td colspan="2"><span>It's no drop.
<br />

<br />
You can sell it back to a vendor (not any vendor, special one).  You will take a hit on the resale of course.
<br />

<br />
It' has been explained to me.. buy either.. the cheapest, or the most expensive.
<br />

<br />
Cheapest gives you the advantages mentioned above.  Most expensive gives you faster-than-sow movement.</span></td>
